Ecology and distribution. It is difficult to establish its bathymetric and geographical distribution due to the uncertainty of some records. It has been found for sure at depths between 24 (
Vervoort 1972 a
) and 400 m (
Millard 1977
). Gonothecae found in April (
Millard 1977
) and June (
Vervoort 1972 a
).
